      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "hey prof, i'm stuck on this tree diagram for my homework. if i have the sentence \"i saw the man with the telescope,\" why does the PP \"with the telescope\" sometimes attach to the VP instead of the NP? like, what's the actual rule for deciding which branch it goes on?",
      "beast_suffix": "",
